{{for|the playable character from {{XCX|-}}|L'cirufe}} {{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = L |image = Consul L human.png |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Male |haircolor = |eyecolor = |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = }} '''L''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == L is a [[Consul]]. He destroyed [[Colony 5]] once it became Gold Rank, though it is unknown if he was assigned as its Consul.
He first appears in his Moebius form killing [[Orsolya]], [[X]] didn't really care about L, calling him an underling. [[Ouroboros]], [[Riku]], [[Manana]], and [[Bolearis]] defeated L, though X escaped.
== Appearance == Despite never appearing outside of his [[Moebius]] form in-game, L's human design was revealed in the ''Xenoblade Chronicles 3 Collector's Edition'' artbook. L sports a tall and very slender build. His Consul helmet resembles an Anubis head, with prominent pointed jackal ears and a jackal snout above his forehead. {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Moebius L |image = Consul L.jpg |caption = Moebius L |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Moebius]] |level = 47 |area = [[Urayan Trail]] ([[Loska Plateau]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Side Story: Eunie]]'' |respawn = No |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 2,136 |cp = 300 |sp = 0 |gold = 0 |hp = 1,716,800 |strength = 554 |ether = 303 |dexterity = 190 |agility = 161 |physdef = 0% |ethdef = 0% |critrate = 0% |guardrate = 0% }} '''Moebius L''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] who is a [[Moebius]] and can be found at level 47 at [[Loska Plateau]] on the [[Urayan Trail]] during ''[[Side Story: Eunie]]''. He fights alongside [[X|Consul X]].
